-- Erste plays down additional impact of Hungary FX loans
-- By Michael Shields
-- Thu Oct 30, 2014 04:16AM EDT
-- None



VIENNA, Oct 30 (Reuters) - Erste Group <ERST.VI> does not expect any further substantial hit in Hungary if the country converts foreign-currency loans into local forints next year as expected, Chief Executive Andreas Treichl told a conference call on Thursday.

